latestPosts.caption: restocking and picking up some items from @ultabeauty
Im a toe side warrior 🥲 but this last snow trip I was able to learn heel side!

They make great souvenirs for friends/family! we went to like 4 locations. 
Sizes and charms are available depending on the day and locations you go to. 
You choose your shoes then your charms and pay. After you pay they’ll put on the charms for you. Or if you have a belt hole puncher at home, you can do it at home.
it was so hot but it was worth it
got to leave a little piece of us in Brazil 🇧🇷❤️
the slopes kicked our butts but learning new hobbies as an adult is so fun. Better late than never.
